gText_Truck_Intro::
	.string "{COLOR DARK_GRAY}The moving truck rumbles\n"
	.string "along the winding road to\l"
	.string "LITTLEROOT TOWN…{COLOR DARK_GRAY}\p"
	.string "You sit quietly among the boxes.\n"
	.string "Watching the HOENN countryside\l"
	.string "roll by through the small window.\p"
	.string "The DRIVER glances back through\n"
	.string "the rear window.\p"
	.string "{COLOR BLUE}DRIVER: Pretty quiet back there, kid.\n"
	.string "Nervous about the move?\p"
	.string "{COLOR GREEN}{PLAYER}: A little, I guess.\p"
	.string "It's been a while since we've moved\l"
	.string "somewhere new.{COLOR DARK_GRAY}\p"
	.string "{COLOR BLUE}DRIVER: HOENN's a good place for\n"
	.string "fresh starts. I've been driving this\l"
	.string "route for years.\p"
	.string "Starting over can be a good thing\n"
	.string "sometimes, you know?\p"
	.string "{COLOR GREEN}{PLAYER}: Starting over, huh?\p"
	.string "If only it was that easy…{COLOR DARK_GRAY}$"

gText_Truck_MysteriousBox::
	.string "An old wooden box with strange\n"
	.string "symbols carved into its surface.\p"
	.string "{COLOR GREEN}{PLAYER}: What's with this box?\p"
	.string "These symbols look ancient.{COLOR DARK_GRAY}\p"
	.string "{COLOR BLUE}DRIVER: Oh, that old thing?\n"
	.string "Found it in storage. Previous\l"
	.string "owner left it.\p"
	.string "Figured someone might want it.\p"
	.string "The box feels warm to the touch,\n"
	.string "despite the cool air in the truck.\p"
	.string "{COLOR GREEN}{PLAYER}: It's… glowing slightly.\p"
	.string "That's not normal, is it?{COLOR DARK_GRAY}\p"
	.string "{COLOR BLUE}DRIVER: HOENN's full of strange\n"
	.string "things, kid. You'll get used to it.$"

gText_Truck_DevenCorpBox::
	.string "A sleek metallic container\n"
	.string "bearing the DEVON CORPORATION logo.\p"
	.string "{COLOR GREEN}{PLAYER}: DEVON CORPORATION?\p"
	.string "What kind of company is that?{COLOR DARK_GRAY}\p"
	.string "{COLOR BLUE}DRIVER: Big tech company in\n"
	.string "RUSTBORO. They make all sorts of\l"
	.string "gadgets for trainers.\p"
	.string "Oh, that reminds me! There's\n"
	.string "something in there I found after\l"
	.string "my last delivery from them.\p"
	.string "Inside, you spot a peculiar\n"
	.string "bracelet with a crystalline\l"
	.string "centerpiece.\p"
	.string "{COLOR BLUE}DRIVER: They said I could keep it\n"
	.string "if I wanted, but jewelry's not\l"
	.string "really my style.\p"
	.string "You can have it if you like, kid.\p"
	.string "Looks like it'd suit a young\l"
	.string "trainer better than an old driver.\p"
	.string "{PLAYER} obtained the MEGA RING!\p"
	.string "{COLOR GREEN}{PLAYER}: This bracelet feels…\p"
	.string "familiar somehow. Like it's been\l"
	.string "waiting for me.{COLOR DARK_GRAY}\p"
	.string "{COLOR BLUE}DRIVER: Huh, that's interesting.\n"
	.string "Maybe it was meant to be yours.$"

gText_Truck_MemoryBox::
	.string "A simple cardboard box labeled\n"
	.string "'MEMORIES' in your mother's\l"
	.string "handwriting.\p"
	.string "{COLOR GREEN}{PLAYER}: Mom packed our old\n"
	.string "photos and stuff in here.{COLOR DARK_GRAY}\p"
	.string "{COLOR BLUE}DRIVER: Memories are important.\p"
	.string "But don't let them hold you back\l"
	.string "from making new ones.\p"
	.string "HOENN's got plenty of adventures\n"
	.string "waiting for someone like you.\p"
	.string "{COLOR GREEN}{PLAYER}: Someone like me?{COLOR DARK_GRAY}\p"
	.string "{COLOR BLUE}DRIVER: Trust me, kid. The\n"
	.string "POKéMON here can sense things about\l"
	.string "people that even we don't know about\l"
	.string "ourselves.$"

gText_Truck_PlayerReflection::
	.string "{COLOR BLUE}DRIVER: Whatever you're leaving\n"
	.string "behind, HOENN has a way of helping\l"
	.string "people find their true path.\p"
	.string "{COLOR GREEN}{PLAYER}: You really think so?{COLOR DARK_GRAY}\p"
	.string "{COLOR BLUE}DRIVER: I've seen it happen\n"
	.string "before. Young trainers come here\l"
	.string "carrying all sorts of burdens…\p"
	.string "But there's something special about\n"
	.string "this region. The legends say the\l"
	.string "land itself chooses its champions.\p"
	.string "{COLOR GREEN}{PLAYER}: Champions, huh…{COLOR DARK_GRAY}$"

gText_Truck_ReadyToExit::
	.string "The truck begins to slow down.\p"
	.string "{COLOR BLUE}DRIVER: Here we are!\n"
	.string "LITTLEROOT TOWN! Time to start that\l"
	.string "new chapter of yours!\p"
	.string "{COLOR GREEN}{PLAYER}: Thanks for the ride…\p"
	.string "and the advice. And the bracelet.{COLOR DARK_GRAY}\p"
	.string "{COLOR BLUE}DRIVER: Don't mention it, kid.\p"
	.string "Something tells me you're going\l"
	.string "to need it.\p"
	.string "{COLOR GREEN}{PLAYER}: Here goes nothing…{COLOR DARK_GRAY}$"
